    Regression Module¶

    In [1]:
    from mygeopackage import *
from mygeopackage.regression import ols
    In [2]:
    json2 = Geo(r'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/yungming0119/mygeopackage/main/docs/notebooks/data/boston.geojson')
    In [3]:
    results = ols(json2,11,[9],0)
    In [4]:
    results.show()
    Make this Notebook Trusted to load map: File -> Trust Notebook
